data.description: PRICE REDUCED!! MOTIVATED SELLER!! Move-in ready, beautifully updated duplex featuring three bedrooms and two and a half baths. This remarkable home boasts a galley kitchen enhanced with granite countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, and a built-in microwave. Additionally, it offers an electric oven and a separate laundry room for utmost convenience. The dining room has elegant bay windows allowing natural light to flow through. You'll find the master bedroom, complete with a walk-in closet and an attached bath featuring granite counters, an under-mounted sink, and a separate shower. Two more bedrooms and an additional full bath are also located on the upper level. The property includes an attached two-car garage with a rear entry and a lovely yard encased by a fresh wooden fence. This sensational home is waiting for you!
